      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it that it's basically pristine inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s as close to new as you can get without the massive price tag, this is the one for you! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
