    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides precise tactile engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a proactive rod bearing service using VAC coated shells. The suspension retains its factory-correct kinematics with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. Every surface, from the Nappa leather bolsters to the pristine undercarriage, reflects meticulous preservation. Zero deferred maintenance; a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
