      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. This vehicle is in flawless condition, boasting a 100% original factory finish with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. The interior is equally pristine, featuring untouched leather bolsters, original floor mats, and a smoke-free cabin that still retains its new-car scent. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. I have maintained a comprehensive binder of all service records, showing strictly scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle with a clean title and no history of accidents or modifications. I welcome and encourage pre-purchase inspections at any local specialist to confirm this car's exceptional state.",
